{"tid":1537803,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警世】請文宣唔冇亂整文宣!","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:07:00.000Z","uid":125727,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"863362bc0941da1de146dfe9d38df41b3a4226b5","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"留意到已家好多文宣成日帶方向  而且時間極倉促, 話搞就搞<br />\n<br />\n例如「九二九三, 三罷」都只係1個星期內出文宣, 話搞就搞 ,  結果其實得罷課搞到  完全自欺欺人.<br />\n已家又吹風今個星期又搞機場交通壓力測試,  上次差d被大圍捕, 今次同一招係極大風險!<br />\n<br />\n只係想大家唔冇盲目跟從文宣圖既運動!  最慘已家根本肯主動參加每場運動都係勇武  但整文宣既人就缺席 又吸納唔到和理非參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敵人有心搞散你  都可以求其整張文宣圖帶風向,<br />\n話搞就搞係無大台既過程, 但結果可以衰落得好快!<br />\n<br />\n文宣必須要衡量  「<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">隨著運動發展</span></strong>」既大原則下,<br />\n考慮1.時間   2.時機   3.針對目標  4.運動風向  5.民情共識  6.可行性及成效"},{"pid":"4bbadcc5d938d51394fbcfeacab7c0802e4dd52e","tid":1537803,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee8845eb7f63572f137c008a90465236c3decf14","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc9996e3d6b98bc86e94a7d9becff8d89e70834","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d7a132d61d80d06b52539086cc17b78cfd33bf","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543320bf98c15ece429c0935756e7d70b06697a6","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e023504d9cb29d0ff10e6a82602bd236245dd9","tid":1537803,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src